'''英國邊境管理局'''（{{lang-en|UK Border Agency}}，{{lang|en|UKBA}}）是一個已廢除的[[英國政府|英國政府]][[邊境管制|邊境管制]]機構，屬於[[內政部_(英國)|內政部]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-border-agency |title=UK Border Agency |year=2013 |publisher=GOV.UK |accessdate=27 March 2013}}</ref> 2008年4月1日作為一個[[執行機構|執行機構]]成立，是由[[邊境和移民管理局|邊境和移民管理局]]、UKvisas以及[[稅務海關總署|稅務海關總署]]合併而成的。<ref>"[http://www.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/border_review.aspx Security in a global hub – Establishing the UK’s new border arrangements] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120801122855/www.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/border_review.aspx |date=2012-08-01 }}". Cabinet Office. Last updated 16 June 2009.</ref>

其下主要分為四個部門，分別負責運營、移民和定居、國際運營以及[[簽證|簽證]]和法律執行。<ref name="Org">{{cite web |url=http://ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk/aboutus/organisation/ |title=Our organisation |year=2013 |publisher=UK Border Agency |accessdate=27 March 2013}}</ref>

該機構被[[議會和健康服務專員|議會專員]]批為長期服務不佳、積壓數千樁案件并受到大量抱怨。<ref name="faf">[http://www.ombudsman.org.uk/__data/assets/tpdf_file/0016/673/UKBA-2010-02-09.pdf Fast and Fair?]{{dead link|date=October 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }} – report on UK Border Agency by the Parliamentary Ombudsman, published 9 February 2010</ref> 而這些抱怨主要來自移民申請者和難民。<ref name="omb">{{cite web |url=http://www.ombudsman.org.uk/about-us/media-centre/press-releases/2010/pr2010-03 |title=Press release: Ombudsman publishes report on UK Border Agency |publisher=Ombudsman.org.uk |accessdate=12 April 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120403030127/http://www.ombudsman.org.uk/about-us/media-centre/press-releases/2010/pr2010-03 |archivedate=3 April 2012 }}</ref>

2013年3月26日，英國內政部的[[文翠珊|文翠珊]]宣佈該機構將被廢除，工作交由內政部直接負責。31日撤銷其執行機構的地位。<ref name=AgencyStatusRevoked>{{cite web|url=http://www.theyworkforyou.com/debates/?id=2013-03-26b.1500.0 |title=UK Border Agency |publisher=UK Parliament Hansard via TheyWorkForYou.com |date=26 March 2013 |accessdate=8 June 2013}}</ref><ref name=UKBATransition>{{cite web |url=http://www.ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk/sitecontent/newsarticles/2013/may/11-transition |title=UK Border Agency’s transition to Home Office   |publisher=Former UK Border Agency Website |date=3 May 2013 |accessdate=8 June 2013 |archive-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616175953/http://www.ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk/sitecontent/newsarticles/2013/may/11-transition |dead-url=no }}</ref> 原機構的職能被分成管理簽證和移民的和管理移民法律執行的兩個不同組織。<ref name=Abolition>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-21941395 |title=UK Border Agency 'not good enough' and being scrapped |publisher=BBC News |date=26 March 2013 |accessdate=26 March 2013}}</ref><ref>[http://www.ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk/aboutus/organisation/ UK Border Agency | Our organisation]. Ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk (2013-04-01). Retrieved on 2013-10-23.</ref>

